ctrl + d --> copy line down
ctrl + e --> copy line down 

alt + cursors --> for multiple cursors
ctrl + b --> to open/close the explorer

shift + cursor --> to select the text from previous cursor to new cursor
ctrl + home/end --> to go at the top/bottom of the program
ctrl + shift + home/end --> to select from that point to top/bottom

alt + shift + cursor--> for multiple arrows together in straight up or straight down position

shift + up --> move line up
shift + down --> move line down

ctrl + j --> Terminal